00:09:56.486 --> 00:09:57.596 A:middle
a language like Arabic and

00:09:57.596 --> 00:09:57.966 A:middle
Hebrew.

00:09:58.696 --> 00:09:59.806 A:middle
And this means that with Auto

00:09:59.806 --> 00:10:01.336 A:middle
Layout you can create these

00:09:59.806 --> 00:10:01.336 A:middle
